citations:
    citation-asos-daenerys-ii:
        source: source-asos
        properties:
            locator: "Daenerys II"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Daenerys arrives at Astapor. Inspects Unsullied on the Plaza of Pride. Good Master Kraznys mo Nakloz shows her the Unsullied — their training regimen, their castration, the 'wine of courage' that suppresses pain, the naming-disk system. Missandei acts as translator between Kraznys and Daenerys. Daenerys feigns ignorance of High Valyrian. Arstan Whitebeard objects to buying slaves. Daenerys cannot yet decide."
